type: Superalgos Review - Next Level Tutorials and Documentation

definition.text: An amazing project that follows the FOSS philosophy. It has a steep learning curve, but with the well crafted tutorials and detailed documentation, it's easy to get started.

paragraphs.text: After discovering Superalgos I felt super intimidated by all the different nodes and giant trees of nodes working together, but after going through the first two tutorials, I already feel more confident. I can't wait to start experimenting with different strategies and deploy Superalgos on my home server. I will try to contribute as much as I can.
